Class CollectionFactory

java.lang.Object
  jaitools.jiffle.util.CollectionFactory

public class CollectionFactory
extends java.lang.Object

Some convenience methods to create generic collections following the DRY (Don't Repeat Yourself) principle. Examples of use: List list1 = CollectionFactory.newList(); List> list2 = CollectionFactory.newList();
